<figureCitation captionStart="FIGURES 113–118" captionStartId="41.[151,264,1368,1393]" captionTargetBox="[154,1432,313,1338]" captionTargetId="figure@41.[151,1436,308,1343]" captionTargetPageId="41" captionText="FIGURES 113–118. Male genitalia of Schaffnerocoris spp. S. fuscotibialis, n. sp.: 113, right paramere. 114, left paramere. S. pallipes, n. sp.: 115, left paramere. 116, right paramere. S. tibiopallidus, n. sp.: 117, left paramere. 118, right paramere." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3816486" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3816486/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="210">Figs. 113, 115, 117</figureCitation>
